flowchart TD
    Start[Execute Phase] --> ParseManifest[Read Phase Manifest]
    ParseManifest --> Wave1[Identify Generation 0 / Wave 1 Plans]
    Wave1 --> ParallelExecute[Execute Plans in Parallel]
    
    subgraph Execution Node
        ReadPlan[Read XX-YY-PLAN.md]
        WriteCode[Code Generation]
        RunTests[Running Tests]
        SelfCheck[Generate SUMMARY.md]
        Commit[Git Commit - atomic]
        
        ReadPlan --> WriteCode
        WriteCode --> RunTests
        RunTests --> SelfCheck
        SelfCheck --> Commit
    end
    
    ParallelExecute --> ExecutionNode1[Agent 1 executing Plan X]
    ParallelExecute --> ExecutionNode2[Agent 2 executing Plan Y]
    
    ExecutionNode1 --> Wait
    ExecutionNode2 --> Wait
    
    Wait[Wait for Wave to Complete] --> CheckNextWaves{More Waves Remaining?}
    CheckNextWaves -- Yes --> NextWave[Identify Generation N+1 Plans]
    NextWave --> ParallelExecute
    CheckNextWaves -- No --> Complete[Phase Completed]
